
# Agents

This folder contains the agent definitions and workflows used in SDLC Foundry.

## Agents

### Agent 1 - Requirement Analyzer
Analyzes BRDs, SOPs, and process walkthrough transcripts to extract process understanding, applications, business rules, and exceptions.

### Agent 2 - PDD Generator
Generates Process Definition Document (PDD)  drafts from analyzed requirements.

### Agent 3 - SDD Generator
Generates Solution Design Document (SDD)  drafts from analyzed requirements.

### Agent 4 - Architecture Planner
Designs the automation architecture, reusable components, framework recommendation, and workflow structure.

### Agent 5 - Workflow Skeleton Builder
Generates an automation-ready UiPath bot skeleton with activities, placeholders, exception handling, and TODO items.

### Agent 6 - Test Case Generator
Creates functional, negative, and edge-case test scenarios from approved requirements.
